{"tid":447903,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"［對唔住 老豆老母］比起高IQ 我更想要高EQ","createTime":"2017-10-25T17:25:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-26T17:46:31.000Z","uid":24817,"like":3,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ca545b399d52836faf233add4c72e361359a56c7","tid":447903,"uid":24817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T17:25:00.000Z","msg":"細細個覺得高iq先係王道，夠聰明就可以解決好多問題<br />\n到大個左先覺得，自己最缺既係Eq<br />\n成日都恃住有小聰明 係某啲時候會嫌人蠢又剩 對住朋友就係心入面講 但對住屋企人唔知點解就會好易扯火<br />\n<br />\n其實有時唔係人地蠢 可能係諗法唔同令到大家做法唔同<br />\n可能自己既做法係快、令、正<br />\n但人地有自己做法比較安心啲，又無可不可姐<br />\n點解當時又嫌人地蠢<br />\n就算人地真係蠢咁又點 你比人聰明都唔代表可以燥人<br />\n更何況果個係屋企人<br />\n<br />\n今日發生左啲小事 燥左屋企人 而真係好小事<br />\n燥完收線果下好後悔 好自責<br />\n其實佢地跟本無做錯乜 但因為小小事就比人燥<br />\n仲要佢地辛苦左成日番工 番到屋企仲要受個仔氣<br />\n佢地一直對我好好 由細個開始寧願自己瞓廳 都要比間房我<br />\n到依家上到U 比哂學費 宿舍費 生活費（當然第時比家用 我一定唔會比少）<br />\n夜晚佢地比錢我既時候 果刻真係好內疚 <br />\n拎完拎轉面個鼻有啲酸 隻眼有啲紅<br />\n到依家靜靜地就諗起好多對佢地差既時候<br />\n跟住又諗起一食飯佢地關心我既時候<br />\n果個反差 真係好想死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n老豆老母 對唔住 孩兒不考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我真係好想可以高Eq啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後 其實我真係好愛你地嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ba13544213f73fc57ed5b48d0355e2a42c7f49a","tid":447903,"uid":27915,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T17:26:34.000Z","msg":"你父母有上連登？"},{"pid":"f0254f2929fe5c8703f860a5ea5e4ec3704b0adc","tid":447903,"uid":146675,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T17:27:08.000Z","msg":"講有閪用咩 做啦"},{"pid":"15b4eafab328ce2977cc7b526399e3f3d5faf93c","tid":447903,"uid":24817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T17:27:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講有閪用咩 做啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb4a2870bfcc56b01de773f09fe3ccb6ecb25ae8","tid":447903,"uid":24817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T17:28:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你父母有上連登？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好想搵個地方懺悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a60394539bf488a9bb538d29081a3b250d471479","tid":447903,"uid":106523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T17:30:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你父母有上連登？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好想搵個地方懺悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有心懺悔 無心行動？"},{"pid":"d976ca4ddc8bdc30df979fed5eac55df93d14fa1","tid":447903,"uid":24817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T17:34:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你父母有上連登？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好想搵個地方懺悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有心懺悔 無心行動？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當然唔係啦，而係好想彌補之前做既錯事，但我知做錯左就係做錯左，就算我之後做番好都補唔到之前做錯既事<br />\n<br />\n依家唯有就係，想自己生生性性，唔好再錯落去，由發少啲脾氣開始，同埋番屋企既時間考順啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c06388ae76ae14244cb5bc289c8e86cd6dfde6e","tid":447903,"uid":28960,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T17:36:32.000Z","msg":"最撚憎依啲人<br />\n侍住自己聰明就睇人唔起<br />\n有啲連基本禮貌都無<br />\n搵人幫你果陣好似老奉咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔係針對樓主你"},{"pid":"f6192fa83ee6fd30b41647cbc98775409441b8b3","tid":447903,"uid":132898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T17:36:34.000Z","msg":"你覺得喺度講你老豆老母就會知你點諗咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi